entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Find this Selonian agent Taarna spoke of. See if you can help her with her problem. Agent Taarna said it was important to be diplomatic when addressing the Selonians; they are not accustomed to asking for help from strangers.
entries.journal_entry_description: You have been sent to Nashal, Talus in an effort to help the CorSec agent Taarna.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find agent Taarna and see what job he has for you.
